title: Vita Cafe
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, American, International, Beer/Wine, Take-out, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Vegetarian and vegan friendly American comfort food and international cuisine with some organic ingredients used. Large breakfast, lunch, and dinner menus plus a kids' menu. Tofu scrambles, nachos, bean chili, vegan mac n cheese, vegan cakes and burgers, seitan fajita, and more. Full bar. Established in 1999.
